281
00:27:04,833 --> 00:27:06,800
Let's talk.

282
00:27:08,800 --> 00:27:10,533
Okay.

283
00:27:16,767 --> 00:27:21,167
Seung Eon, I've made up my mind.

284
00:27:21,733 --> 00:27:25,367
Now it's your turn. There's something you need to do.

285
00:27:27,767 --> 00:27:32,165
What my mom said about you being an uneducated orphan,

286
00:27:32,800 --> 00:27:35,733
I apologize for that.

287
00:27:35,733 --> 00:27:37,500
Sorry.

288
00:27:37,500 --> 00:27:39,933
But even if you can't help with other things,

289
00:27:39,933 --> 00:27:42,467
you can avoid this with a middle school diploma.

290
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:49,267
You know I have a teaching certificate, right?

291
00:27:49,267 --> 00:27:53,100
I'll help you prepare for the GED.

292
00:27:54,033 --> 00:27:57,033
Think about it and let me know.

293
00:28:02,167 --> 00:28:05,533
Am I supposed to carry the luggage?

294
00:28:14,933 --> 00:28:17,867
   

295
00:28:20,800 --> 00:28:22,220
 Yeon Soo, where are you? 

296
00:28:22,220 --> 00:28:24,560
 Let's meet. I have something to say. 

297
00:28:24,567 --> 00:28:26,700
 Could you let me know when you're available to talk? 

298
00:28:26,700 --> 00:28:29,033
 I think I've been selfish. 

299
00:28:29,033 --> 00:28:31,800
 Contact me, I'll wait. 

300
00:28:31,800 --> 00:28:35,133
 Can we talk for a bit today? 

301
00:28:35,133 --> 00:28:38,767
 I went to the clinic, and you weren't there. 

302
00:28:39,767 --> 00:28:42,467
 Where are you, Yeon Soo? 

303
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:45,867
   

304
00:28:54,933 --> 00:28:56,600
You are here.

305
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:01,033
Baton touch.

306
00:29:01,033 --> 00:29:03,433
You can go now, Mr. Yeon Soo.

307
00:29:03,433 --> 00:29:05,500
I have to be here, we're family.

308
00:29:05,500 --> 00:29:09,433
After getting him admitted, your part is over.

309
00:29:09,433 --> 00:29:13,167
I'll handle the rest as his hospital mate.

310
00:29:13,167 --> 00:29:17,867
- It's okay, still… 
 - Go back, don't worry.

311
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:37,433
I knew this would happen, so I bought it.

312
00:29:42,933 --> 00:29:47,367
Haven't you heard anything from Yeon Soo yet?

313
00:29:55,267 --> 00:29:58,033
Oh? Manager.

314
00:29:58,033 --> 00:30:00,500
The veterinarian came.

315
00:30:16,167 --> 00:30:19,767
We should find an owner before it gets colder.

316
00:30:19,767 --> 00:30:22,367
Sorry, I couldn't pay attention to you.

317
00:30:26,770 --> 00:30:35,470
♫  Mm, stay by my side  ♫

318
00:30:35,470 --> 00:30:38,450
