321
00:30:49,067 --> 00:30:51,633
 Let's not tell Kang Hee. 

322
00:30:51,633 --> 00:30:54,933
 I don't want to make it hard for her. 

323
00:30:54,933 --> 00:30:57,167
I came because I had something to say.

324
00:31:03,133 --> 00:31:05,633
