So, don't get too attached to the cows from now on.

574
00:50:27,567 --> 00:50:29,933
I miss you.

575
00:50:29,933 --> 00:50:32,000
Chil Ddaeng!

576
00:50:32,000 --> 00:50:34,500
Sampa Gwangtteng!

577
00:50:34,500 --> 00:50:36,800
Pinggu!

578
00:50:36,800 --> 00:50:38,567
Kkomak!

