I regret raising cattle.

580
00:50:46,333 --> 00:50:51,133
I had no idea it would be this hard.

581
00:50:55,600 --> 00:50:57,300
Ms. Yoon.

582
00:51:03,800 --> 00:51:06,300
You miss her a lot, don't you?

583
00:51:07,033 --> 00:51:08,500
When, no…

584
00:51:08,500 --> 00:51:11,300
From where did you hear it? No…

