00:58:33,100 --> 00:58:35,633
Yeah, it's been a while.

668
00:58:36,467 --> 00:58:40,000
I saw your father come with Yeon Soo.

669
00:58:40,000 --> 00:58:42,267
Do you know why?

670
00:58:42,267 --> 00:58:44,933
He comes often.

671
00:58:44,933 --> 00:58:48,267
Yeon Soo's grandfather used to be here, too.

672
00:58:48,267 --> 00:58:50,767
But later he was moved to the hospital.

673
00:58:50,767 --> 00:58:54,700
On holidays or such occasions, your father even performs here.

674
00:58:54,700 --> 00:58:58,700
To the elders here, Mr. Chun Pil is like an idol.

675
00:59:00,733 --> 00:59:02,533
Come in.

676
00:59:10,300 --> 00:59:14,767
Wow! Your hair has grown a lot.

677
00:59:15,567 --> 00:59:18,867
Oh, my! It seems like you've got more hair! Have you rejuvenated?

678
00:59:18,867 --> 00:59:20,000
Oh my, really.

679
00:59:20,000 --> 00:59:21,467
Did you eat something good?

680
00:59:21,467 --> 00:59:23,933
Ah, give me some too.

681
00:59:24,800 --> 00:59:26,400
How would you like your hair done?

682
00:59:26,400 --> 00:59:28,100
Nicely?

683
00:59:28,100 --> 00:59:30,933
Didn't I always do it nicely?

684
00:59:30,933 --> 00:59:35,667
- You look pretty no matter what. 
 - She volunteers here every other week.

685
00:59:35,667 --> 00:59:38,133
Yong Su also comes once a month.

686
00:59:40,233 --> 00:59:43,000
Even though Yong Su talks a lot all the time,

687
00:59:43,000 --> 00:59:45,000
he's like MacGyver with his hands.

688
00:59:45,000 --> 00:59:46,433
There's nothing he can't fix.

689
00:59:46,433 --> 00:59:49,667
He fixes everything: boiler, electricity, machines.

690
00:59:49,667 --> 00:59:53,600
Wait, did you eat something that good? Give me some, too.

691
00:59:54,533 --> 00:59:56,167
I…

