698
01:00:31,167 --> 01:00:34,800
The photos are nice. Who took them?

699
01:00:34,833 --> 01:00:36,733
Cha Seung Eon.

700
01:00:36,733 --> 01:00:39,567
The Cha Seung Eon I know?

701
01:00:39,567 --> 01:00:41,567
Is there another Cha Seung Eon besides him?

702
01:00:41,567 --> 01:00:45,767
It was originally your father's responsibility.

