01:01:46,333 --> 01:01:49,167
It's not just any lake.

720
01:01:49,167 --> 01:01:53,033
The sunset view here is amazing, it really is!

721
01:01:53,033 --> 01:01:57,467
That's why I reserved this place a long time ago, really.

722
01:01:58,900 --> 01:02:02,833
Come and see, it's awesome. Look at this.

